  <entry>
    <title>2006考研英语Text4</title>
    <link href="http://iuming.github.io/2020/08/13/2006%E8%80%83%E7%A0%94%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%ADText4/"/>
    <id>http://iuming.github.io/2020/08/13/2006%E8%80%83%E7%A0%94%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%ADText4/</id>
    <published>2020-08-13T12:13:01.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-08-13T12:19:11.923Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="单词"><a href="#单词" class="headerlink" title="单词"></a>单词</h2><p><strong>onward</strong>:向前、前进、前进的</p><p><strong>phony</strong>:假、虚假、伪造</p><p><strong>daffodil</strong>:水仙花</p><p><strong>evil</strong>:罪恶</p><p><strong>skeptical</strong>:怀疑的</p><p><strong>misery</strong>:痛苦</p><p><strong>perpetual</strong>:连绵不断的</p><p><strong>massacre</strong>:屠杀</p><p><strong>innocent</strong>:无辜</p><p><strong>dedicate</strong>:专用</p><p><strong>depicting</strong>:描绘</p><p><strong>ideology</strong>:思想</p><p><strong>worshipper</strong>:崇拜者</p><p><strong>worm</strong>:蛆虫</p><p><strong>bummer</strong>:坏蛋</p><p><strong>anchor</strong>:主持人</p><p><strong>agenda</strong>:任务</p><p><strong>lure</strong>:引诱</p><p><strong>depend on</strong>:指望</p><p><strong>disappointment</strong>:失望</p><p><strong>Memento Mori</strong>:死亡的提醒</p><p><strong>clove</strong>:丁香</p><p><strong>illusion</strong>:错觉</p><p><strong>in the wake of</strong>：在…之后</p><h2 id="句子"><a href="#句子" class="headerlink" title="句子"></a>句子</h2><p><strong>happiness is more than pleasure without pain.</strong></p><p>幸福远不止是没有痛苦的快乐</p><p><strong>you will die, that everything ends, and that happiness comes not in denying this but in living with it.</strong></p><p>你终将死去，一切都会结束，只有接受这一现实，而非一味逃避，才会有幸福。</p><p><strong>It’s a message even more bitter than a clove cigarette, yet, somehow, a breath of fresh air.</strong></p><p>这一启示甚至比叶子烟还苦，但它却是一股清新的气息。</p>]]></content>
    
    
